L,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0),(17,6,'All Terrain Conversion Kit for Street Carbon/Bamboo Series','<h2>All Terrain Conversion Kit for Street Carbon Series Electric Skateboard</h2>\n<p><strong>$349.00</strong>. All Terrain Conversion Kit for Street Carbon Series Street <strong>Electric Skateboard</strong>. </p>\n<p>Convert the Carbon Series Street Electric Skateboard into an All Terrain monster capable of travelling over both normal hard surfaces as well as All Terrain surfaces. The All Terrain Conversion Kit comes with All Terrain axles, wheels, belt, and drive wheel to convert your Carbon Series Street Board to All Terrain version.</p>\n<p>The All Terrain Conversion Kit for the Carbon Series Electric Skateboard will eat up those poor quality footpaths and roads you would not dream of riding your longboard on. Looks, ride, range, and feel; you\'ll love it!</p>',0,349,'roadie_tires_1_large_c14fdf5e-50a2-4f5a-8a09-72ef19a40d63_grande.jpg',NULL,NULL,0,0,'roadie_tires_1_large_c14fdf5e-50a2-4f5a-8a09-72ef19a40d63.jpg',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'all-terrain-conversion-kit-for-carbon-series-board',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,1),(18,6,'Street Conversion Kit for All Terrain Carbon/Bamboo Series','<h2>Street Conversion Kit for All Terrain Carbon Series Electric Skateboard</h2>\n<p><strong>$225.00</strong>. Street Conversion Kit for Carbon Series All Terrain <strong>Electric Skateboard</strong>. Turn your All-Terrain Skateboard into a street version. The Street Conversion Kit comes with Street axles, Abec 11 wheels, belt, and drive wheel to convert your CarbonAT Board to a street version.</p>\n<p>You\'ll love it!</p>',0,225,'DSC_0767_48bee7eb-6f96-4726-9a4e-23c7450b3c58_grande.jpg',NULL,NULL,0,0,'DSC_0767_48bee7eb-6f96-4726-9a4e-23c7450b3c58.jpg',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'street-conversion-kit-for-at-carbon-series',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,1),(19,6,'Remote Controller','<p>Replacement remote compatible with all of our boards.</p>\n<p> </p>',0,65,'